USASPENDING COMPETITIVE INTELLIGENCE FEATURE
==================================================

PROJECT CONTEXT:
We are building GovSignal AI, an AI-assisted procurement intelligence platform.

The platform should help users:
- find government opportunities
- filter valid-fit contracts
- analyze historical award data
- understand who wins similar contracts
- estimate price ranges
- identify incumbents
- detect competition density
- build a stronger case for how to win

This feature focuses specifically on using USAspending data to analyze actual federal award history.

