==================================================
AWARD MATCHING LOGIC
==================================================

When matching historical awards to a current opportunity:

Prioritize matches in this order:

1. Same agency + same PSC + same NAICS
2. Same agency + same PSC
3. Same agency + same NAICS
4. Same PSC + same NAICS nationwide
5. Same keyword cluster + same agency
6. Same keyword cluster nationwide
7. Similar product/service category

Return confidence level:
- High
- Medium
- Low

Do not overstate conclusions when sample size is small.

